              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                To take the third of these first: Justice Hellen analogizes the surviving spelunkers (at p. 64, above) to rape victims because they were forced to commit an act intentionally but against their will. (Is every case really about rape?)<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>(The last sentence is full of emotion......)
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
